\b0\fs46 \cf0 {\listtext	\'95	}7 ounces sugar\
{\listtext	\'95	}1 1/2 tablespoons finely grated orange zest\
{\listtext	\'95	}1/4 teaspoon {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://www.foodterms.com/encyclopedia/salt/index.html"}}{\fldrslt \cf2 \ul \ulc2 kosher salt}}\
{\listtext	\'95	}2 cups freshly squeezed {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "http://www.foodterms.com/encyclopedia/orange/index.html"}}{\fldrslt \cf2 \ul \ulc2 orange}} juice, approximately 2 to 3 pounds oranges\
